data.description: 2 Acres of waterfront property, nestled along the banks of the beautiful Bayou Teche. This estate home is stunning!  300+ year old oak trees provide canopy shade throughout the property. The timeless front porch greets you as you approach the home. Ample parking with a circular drive provides easy access to the home. Step into the Grand Living Room with Soaring Ceiling heights, Pecky Cypress Walls, a Woodburning Fireplace, and large Picture Windows overlooking the spacious backyard. The wet bar is a great addition for entertaining guests.  The kitchen is a Chef's delight! Totally updated and reconfigured with custom cabinetry and built ins. All new appliances with dual fuel range, Under-Cabinet lighting, and new plumbing. The center island is one of a kind with an oversized slab of dolomite stone! Absolutely gorgeous and very functional! The large laundry room and bonus room are located directly off of the kitchen. The bonus room is currently being used as a gym, but the possibilities are endless! Man cave, game room, craft room or even a second living room! The office, formal dining, guest bedroom and bathroom are located downstairs along with the Primary Suite. The primary suite features vaulted ceilings and French doors that allow views of the backyard. Remodeled bathroom with dual vanities, a sitting area, glass shower, standalone tub, and two large closets. 3 additional bedrooms upstairs.  One of which has its own bathroom, and the others share a jack-n-jill. There's a storage room with attic access, great for crafts, or extra holiday storage! The backyard was built for entertainment!  A custom patio equipped with lighting, electrical outlets, and fans situated next to the basketball court, and a new 32x35 workshop. Spend your evenings overlooking the backyard with views of the Bayou Teche as you watch the boats pass by or launch your own kayak!  This home also includes a 24KW Whole House Generator with Upgraded 400AMP transfer switch, 2-car garage with storage, solar film on all windows, whole house water filtration system, and so much more! Schedule your private tour TODAY!
